# 六、这种柱状图的万能句式（超级重要）

---

# 1. 最大值

> X recorded the highest proportion.

> X represented the largest category.

---

# 2. 最小值

> X had the lowest figure.

> X accounted for the smallest proportion.

---

# 3. 相近数据

> X was followed closely by Y.

> The figures for X and Y were similar.

---

# 4. 对比

> By contrast, ...

> Whereas X..., Y...

> Compared with ...

---

# 5. 更受欢迎

> X was more popular than Y.

> X exceeded Y.

> X surpassed Y.

